FBIS3-60115 "jptdd003__l94081" JPRS-TDD-94-003-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 19 January 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY 106 Kg of Hashish Seized in Istanbul, Four Arrested TA1501141194 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1600 GMT 14 Jan 94 TA1501141194 Ankara TRT Television Network Language: Turkish Article Type:BFN [Announcer-read report] [Text] Four members of a narcotics smuggling network were caught with 106 kg of hashish in Istanbul. According to a statement issued by the Istanbul Security Directorate, the hashish was found in a house in Bagcilar ready for marketing. Four persons were detained in connection with the incident.
